  "detailed_description": "<strong>Tackle Bridge Engineering problems like never before!</strong><br><br>You are an Engineer tasked with building Bridges for different types of vehicles from an SUV to a large Truck!<br><br>You are faced with several different scenarios and environments that you would need to solve with 1 common goal among them all... to get the car across the other side!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/d2a8734241488ae9b9d537be383bf907.avif?t=1670764518\" width=500 height=85 /></span><br>13 Different drivable vehicles!<br>Drive the vehicles yourself behind the wheel in the driver seat or in 3rd Person View!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/045e80096842d39c85bbfa5c95216378.avif?t=1670764518\" width=600 height=286 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/6dd690df75137c0db70f76c09653dfde.avif?t=1670764518\" width=500 height=85 /></span><br>Tackle 21 levels with 3 level difficulties and 4 special levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/0f36fbde1412ed3ab87df07111f7db80.poster.avif?t=1670764518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/0f36fbde1412ed3ab87df07111f7db80.webm?t=1670764518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/0f36fbde1412ed3ab87df07111f7db80.mp4?t=1670764518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/965ddff76a8eaf97ce888398b3f70112.avif?t=1670764518\" width=500 height=85 /></span><br>Take advantage of 30+ items in your tool to make your idea into a Virtual Reality solution and build your ideal Bridge!<br><br>Take some time to relax in your own office space!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205090/extras/53f5484c427fff3330b1508d30acce92.avif?t=1670764518\" width=637 height=329 /></span><br><br><u>Are you ready to earn your \"BRIDGINEER\" Title?</u>",
